## Example Usage

{{< chooser language "typescript,python,go,csharp" / >}}

{{% example csharp %}}
```csharp
using Pulumi;
using SpotInst = Pulumi.SpotInst;

class MyStack : Stack
{
    public MyStack()
    {
        var myTarget = new SpotInst.Multai.Target("myTarget", new SpotInst.Multai.TargetArgs
        {
            BalancerId = "b-12345",
            Host = "host",
            Port = 1338,
            Tags = 
            {
                new SpotInst.Multai.Inputs.TargetTagArgs
                {
                    Key = "env",
                    Value = "prod",
                },
            },
            TargetSetId = "l-98765",
            Weight = 1,
        });
    }

}
```

{{% /md %}}</dd>

</dl>
{{% /choosable %}}
